description._en_: Need simple session management? Several users on the same Chrome? FreshStart is a simple cross browser session manager.
description.es: ¿Necesita gestionar sesiones de manera sencilla? ¿Varios usuarios en el mismo Chrome? FreshStart es un sencillo administrador de sesiones entre varios navegadores.
description.fr: Besoin d'un gestionnaire de session simple? Plusieurs utilisateurs sur le même Chrome? FreshStart est un simple gestionnaire de browser compatible avec différents navigateurs.
description.it: Hai bisogno di una gestione semplice delle sessioni? Molti utenti sullo stesso Chrome? FreshStart è un semplice gestore di sessioni browser.
description.nl: Kunt u wel een simpele Sessie manager gebruiken? Heeft u meerdere gebruikers op Chrome? Dan is FreshStart de oplossingen, de simpele Sessie manager.
description.pt: Precisa de um simples gerenciador de sessões? Tem muitos usuários em um só Chrome? FreshStart é um simples gerenciador de sessões multi-navegador.

snapshotHint._en_: * 'Snapshot #1' up to 'Snapshot #5' are sessions that are saved in an earlier Chrome use. You may find them helpful if the most recent session is corrupted or is not exactly what you want.
